Package kaitech.api.database

Interface MenuItemTable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MenuItemTblImpl
    public interface MenuItemTable
    The MenuItemTable interface declares required functionality to store, retrieve, and modify MenuItems in the database.

    • Method Summary

    • Method Detail

      • getMenuItem

        MenuItem getMenuItem​(java.lang.String code)
        Retrieves a MenuItem from the cache. If the MenuItem does not currently exist in the cache, query the database for the MenuItem. If the query is successful, add the MenuItem to the cache and return it.
        Parameters:
        code - The string code of the ingredient to retrieve.
        Returns:
        An Ingredient if the ingredient exists, null if it does not or cannot be retrieved.

      • getAllIMenuItemCodes

        java.util.Set<java.lang.String> getAllIMenuItemCodes()
        Get all MenuItem codes currently in the database.
        Returns:
        A set of MenuItem codes.

      • putMenuItem

        MenuItem putMenuItem​(MenuItem from)
        Saves a given MenuItem to the database, and returns a database managed MenuItem which is responsible for the automatic saving of changes on setter calls.
        Parameters:
        from - The MenuItem to be saved.
        Returns:
        Database managed MenuItem responsible for automatic saving on setter calls.

      • removeMenuItem

        void removeMenuItem​(java.lang.String code)
        Remove a MenuItem from the database and cache.
        Parameters:
        code - The code of the MenuItem to be removed.

      • resolveAllMenuItems

        java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​MenuItem> resolveAllMenuItems()
        Gets all MenuItem objects from the database. Warning: this can be a costly operation when everything isn't already cached, please use with care.
        Returns:
        A map from code to MenuItem.

      • getOrAddItem

        default MenuItem getOrAddItem​(MenuItem from)
        From a given MenuItem, gets or creates the database equivalent.
        Parameters:
        from - The MenuItem to have its database equivalent retrieved or added.
        Returns:
        Database managed MenuItem responsible for automatic saving on setter calls.
